    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieved level 2 against a required level of 3 due to single loading-rate testing; this gap is accepted given the static, rate-insensitive nature of the COU and the conservative nature of the single test condition relative to in vivo loading. All three primary QoIs satisfy the pre-established acceptance bounds. The credibility package is accepted for submission in support of the 510(k) regulatory decision.",
